# bridge-state/

This directory holds the state files written by the friday-clickup-bridge workflow.
Each file represents one Slack audit message awaiting human replies.

Schema, one file per client per ISO week:
  bridge-state/{client-slug}-{YYYY-Www}.json
  {
    "client": "Cognism",
    "channel_id": "C02R19DLFFE",
    "message_ts": "1736784000.123456",
    "iso_week": "2026-W19",
    "posted_at": "2026-05-09T15:30:00Z",
    "flags": [
      {
        "position": 1,
        "task_id": "abc123",
        "task_url": "https://app.clickup.com/t/abc123",
        "current_value": null,
        "suggested_value": "Product Scoring",
        "resolved": false,
        "resolved_at": null,
        "outcome": null
      }
    ]
  }

Resolved files migrate to bridge-state/archive/ once every flag has an outcome.
